      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not suitable for daily driving. The engine has a persistent loud knocking sound and struggles to maintain idle, suggesting a need for a major overhaul or replacement. Additionally, the transmission is slipping badly, and there is visible rust on the frame along with several large dents on the body panels. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts.",
