      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerfully, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
