    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a 981-chassis mid-engine coupe powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This driver-centric build features a tactile 6-speed manual transmission paired with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for sophisticated damping control. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve peaking at 5,800 RPM, while the mechanical limited-slip differential and Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV) ensure exceptional rotation through the apex. The chassis integrity is superb, showing no signs of fatigue, and the hydraulic-assist steering rack provides precise feedback. Recent service includes a full fluid flush and a clean DME report. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the VarioCam Plus timing and AOS\u2014are in excellent operating condition.",
