      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect blend of luxury and dependable performance. The exterior finish maintains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard is free of any cracks or sun damage. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have followed a rigorous maintenance schedule, with the most recent service involving a comprehensive fluid flush, new brake rotors, and a fresh set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts seamlessly, and has been kept in a smoke-free and pet-free environment. This is a reliable, well-documented car that is ready for the road today.",
